{"tid":181201,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有《深夜食堂》沒關係，準備好宵夜配這 3 部美食日劇吧！","createTime":"2017-03-31T12:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T03:19:04.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"844744de0ebb1aa6436add3905f2a27311c7b610","tid":181201,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"《深夜食堂》、《孤獨的美食家》看完後感覺陷入劇荒啦，吃點宵夜、喝點小酒再配部美食日劇，下班後就是要這樣慵懶到底啊！（理直氣壯！) 不想太燒腦所以小品劇最剛好，推薦下面這三部美食日劇，記得節制可以不用帶、腦袋也可以不用帶，但宵夜一定得準備好，否則半夜餓醒！<br />\n<br />\n《只要有北齋和飯》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db16b0e5632.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db16b0e5632.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=886311bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女主角文子由《你的名字》女主角三葉的配音上白石萌音主演，改變自同名美食漫畫的《只要有北齋和飯》描述個性內向的文子，興趣不是逛市場就是做菜，總會一邊做菜一邊跟布娃娃北齋閒聊，在這過程中做出一道道美味料理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db163bb6196.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db163bb6196.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=cb3ad10f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼所以片名才會叫「只要有北齋和飯」啊～不過總不能只跟布偶演戲，劇裡還是與其他演員有不少對手戲啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KoioDlX5mRY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKoioDlX5mRY&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0435ab67\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KoioDlX5mRY</a><br />\n<br />\n▼對照下面將介紹的兩部，這部最適合女生看，看著軟萌妹子用著幸福的表情做出下面這一道道美味料理，一定超好吃吧～<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db163aeca74.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db163aeca74.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=2f8fc89e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼哈哈陷阱就在這裡！這部美食小品最特別的就是完全沒有「吃料理」的畫面，只到做完料理後就結束當集，讓你看完以後忍不住大吞口水回想「那道料理到底會有多美味呢？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db1640d7a23.gif?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db1640d7a23.gif%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=97c96f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db16385d57d.gif?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db16385d57d.gif%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=08c7e4df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsTnk60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsTnk60.jpg&h=8c13958e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db16375de0c.gif?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db16375de0c.gif%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=7dcef518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼不過劇組也貼心（還是心虛 XD）的為想自己做菜的劇迷與日本食譜網站合作推出了教學影片，看完劇後手癢想自己試試看也是沒問題的啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/spooonn.tv/videos/1336080193123230/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fspooonn.tv%2Fvideos%2F1336080193123230%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e195ff34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/spooonn.tv/videos/1336080193123230/</a><br />\n<br />\n《俠飯》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db1639a2cd0.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db1639a2cd0.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=feee85fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這一部可就是純男人的料理啦，因為養傷暫時躲到宅宅大學生家中的黑道老大，由日劇老面孔生瀨勝久主演，臉上畫著猙獰刀疤的老大把人家家當自己家，任性的用宅宅的廚房做出一道又一道男子漢料理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db1636d6c0a.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db1636d6c0a.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=96b4318f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為什麼說是男子漢料理呢，從隨手可得的食材及大咧咧的烹調手法就能看出「老大」的架勢，以第一集的料理為例，宅宅大學生家一點像樣的食材都沒有，老大卻能變出一桌和食，毛豆跟竹輪煎成的天婦羅配上烤罐頭沙丁魚。<br />\n<br />\n▼聽起來很普通，重點是料理手法啊！再大口的挖一口青蔥飯配啤酒，再大的壓力都消除殆盡啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db163c64467.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db163c64467.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=99d711db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼神奇的是雖然是男子漢料理卻充滿了主婦才懂得生活智慧，像下面這道 A5 牛排，如果不是宅宅親眼所見根本無法想像它本來是要被丟掉的即期肉品，因為放了洋蔥醃漬而有了高級肉的柔嫩口感，這種鐵漢的反差會讓人越看越涮嘴啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db1638c4e95.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db1638c4e95.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=bb5eebe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db1d7e5af69.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db1d7e5af69.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a267a47a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《武士美食家》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r8lvlgu8Qa4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr8lvlgu8Qa4&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=aee9e5a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r8lvlgu8Qa4</a><br />\n這部是三月中才在 Netflix 上架的新劇，一樣是找來老戲骨竹中直人主演，若說前面兩部都是藉由料理的過程治癒大家，《武士美食家》比較偏向《孤獨的美食家》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db163dc22c0.gif?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db163dc22c0.gif%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=850585fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情描述退休後的大叔，因為突然空閒下來選擇把獨自用餐當成種冒險四處挑戰，不過跟《孤獨的美食家》比較不一樣的是，松重豐的五郎比較不會跟餐廳裡的人有互動，總是專注於品嚐自己眼前的美食，竹中大叔的角色因為是個退休阿伯對於人生未來都帶有些迷茫，劇情安排他藉由美食冒險的過程感受人生百態進而找到生活目標。<br />\n<br />\n▼《武士美食家》結合美食和搞笑的方式讓觀眾們知道「中年退休症候群」其實沒有想像中的可怕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64218/58db1637d19f9.gif?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64218%2F58db1637d19f9.gif%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=3bdf387e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好啦，大道理講太多沒用，《武士美食家》裡的美食因為是四處冒險，類型也相當豐富，從居酒屋、便當、義大利麵到日式關東煮應有盡有，好了話不多說，準備好你的止饑食物，一起來看劇吧！"},{"pid":"ebeab7b4ce232044b3dd81c04b8e635141f62f19","tid":181201,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"好似好正wo"},{"pid":"44e136bfedbfbf795900c2339e6f008c48267c1c","tid":181201,"uid":44970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:48:57.000Z","msg":"入嚟為左睇朱千雪"},{"pid":"8eeb31a231c38f83002651317cafbd555089ac94","tid":181201,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"頭2套都有睇<br />\n<br />\n生瀨勝久做得好型"},{"pid":"51348b709c680ee7d29e5d8a509814f54e12982c","tid":181201,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"上白石萌音同朱千雪都幾似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9086ae3320b0653fe2db9b468f798a1369ebb2b0","tid":181201,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"萌音BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ff17852db5f77ba55d499f43afbea5d3c6a977","tid":181201,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:06:36.000Z","msg":"俠飯夠貼地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c5d659fb4223e62f189c6de6b4e6aba9901fed","tid":181201,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"日本人咁食法<br />\n好易變肥佬"},{"pid":"8c3266e0458295ba9b9e3f8e7a4105eeb6bf6600","tid":181201,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"好想睇+食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f762054e5d036cb0b616fd2c55c10007c5a7b35f","tid":181201,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本人咁食法<br />\n好易變肥佬</blockquote><br />\n但日本又唔算多肥佬肥婆"},{"pid":"6eafe60ae8326a34b4d1705012fc195365e85f96","tid":181201,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T19:19:18.000Z","msg":"深夜食堂幾時出5<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20005ecbda4b92f19a016f8cde13da16e56aa9ad","tid":181201,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T19:32:48.000Z","msg":"俠飯幾好睇，女主角唔錯"},{"pid":"484aa4f6de68ee72308b90221ff1b81f605bd9e1","tid":181201,"uid":22902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"俠飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}